{"tid":1297915,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真Post] 必須檢討連登作為運動平台潛在危險","createTime":"2019-07-08T17:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T09:08:01.000Z","uid":199292,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"64abf550b4733a41b1a582554076644d423583d8","tid":1297915,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"成場運動最多人講嘅就係無大台，但其實無大台之下有平台<br />\nTg同呢度好明顯係場運動入面民間自發最大號召同影響力嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n而今晚件事可以睇得出，場運動已經出現極大危機<br />\n<br />\n以下係引起嘅一啲思考：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 運動極度依靠連登</span></span></strong><br />\n之前ddos熄燈已經睇到，一旦連登不能夠發揮正常作用，策略就已經容易無法討論<br />\n如果以後有一大堆3毛發動總攻狼來了多幾次以後就冇人信(或者可能今次已經係)<br />\n等於廢晒所有連登武功<br />\n之前有人講過話8chan, ptt等等 <br />\n都冇乜人知甚至介面需要時間去適應，就算用嚟做方舟都有一段時間會冇晒所有討論<br />\n所以個人覺得呢個一定要思考，如果唔係一冇左連登就死<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 大家正評之前唔該諗清楚</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n拿好老實講，今晚唔可以瀨晒出假膠post嘅人<br />\n正評嘅都有責任<br />\n呢度唔係facebook，唔好當正評=like=已讀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正評係非常帶動風向</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">咁應該點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>1. 唔好妄想可以逃避到敵方間諜收風，要加強內部溝通只可以靠現場決定</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n狗一定有account睇到加密內容<br />\nTg亦都一定有敵人入到去唔同channel入面<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">基本上我地接觸到嘅資訊，敵人都會接觸到</span></strong><br />\n相反好多自己人無account，睇唔到會員加密內容<br />\n加密已經唔再係一個barrier去保障自己人<br />\n至少全部人都要知嘅嘢(e.g.被捕需知)一定唔可以加密<br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁如果有嘢唔想敵方知可以點？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>2. 靠群眾力量去分真假嘅作用已經失效，只能靠自己</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n69咁耐以嚟，點分邊啲post係應該信同唔應該信？<br />\n就係一直靠自己人、正評<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">群眾本身已經block晒所有唔應該出現嘅討論<br />\n但咁係咪一件好事？</span></strong><br />\n唔一定，好似今晚大家都想正評玩膠post，唔理咩原因，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">用群眾做防中伏嘅作用已經失效</span></strong><br />\n所以每個post之前都一定要望清楚，曲直難分嘅最好問下身邊人，問多幾個人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最後！！<br />\n我正式呼籲玩膠post以後唔好再有！！！場運動就咁失敗點對得起支持我地嘅人、同路人同烈士？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">被fake左嘅義士，我明你地依家一定嬲到仆街，但希望大家過埋今晚就當粉筆字抹晒佢！場運動未完，千其唔好灰心！！！</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正如之前有啲自殺post唔知真假，點解明知可能係假都要撲出去？因為做得幾多得幾多！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">五大訴求一定要繼續爭取呀！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不分化、不割蓆、槍口對外，齊上齊落！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3e33e0da868d3c98db49bf4924eed604e762a169","tid":1297915,"uid":199292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2171fe21ac76597b8797c6e7bc88f19596811130","tid":1297915,"uid":40537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:15:35.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係唔好再玩膠post"},{"pid":"76b3d9528eeaf025c768753592a0a7a46979efbc","tid":1297915,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好再玩膠post，亦都唔好再講咩以後唔出去，希望大家體諒！！！繼續努力！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0fcb7da6d79123568fff346675bea88ab83f0296","tid":1297915,"uid":23854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43387dd6db6221a62fce30a5a09a166ed3ba2875","tid":1297915,"uid":1673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"其實真係自己要思考, 唔好信曬連登, 自己決定行動方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a3be0388101eca2fa78fa8f6add0256f1943cf","tid":1297915,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43387dd6db6221a62fce30a5a09a166ed3ba2875","tid":1297915,"uid":1673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"其實真係自己要思考, 唔好信曬連登, 自己決定行動方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:23:23.000Z","msg":"做好fact check都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084a74dc4fc23056e6f69eec1e152c77044f8bea","tid":1297915,"uid":267396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶腦上連登"},{"pid":"57be03967ecf17685793c8ded11de0b73c2d2425","tid":1297915,"uid":1673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6a3be0388101eca2fa78fa8f6add0256f1943cf","tid":1297915,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43387dd6db6221a62f